ae/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eInstagram\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat:\u003c/strong\u003e An apparel, accessories and lifestyle brand that prioritizes using deadstock and natural materials such as \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/leather\"\u003eleather\u003c/a\u003e, bamboo and lyocell.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePrice Range:\u003c/strong\u003e $30-$400\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFounder:\u003c/strong\u003e Faith Winston\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOrigin Story: \u003c/strong\u003eCeres Monae, established in 2022 by founder Faith Winston, derives its name from the goddess of harvest, who represents uniqueness and serves as a protector of the earth. They craft most products in-house in Dallas, TX, offering clothing, accessories and lifestyle products. The brand represents a holistic approach where traditional techniques meet modern sensibilities, resulting in timeless yet forward-thinking pieces.\u003c/p\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll to Continue\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eRecommended Articles\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHero Products:\u003c/strong\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://fave.co/3DnWw7n\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eWhite Dolman Sleeve Dress\u003c/a\u003e ($385)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStockists: \u003c/strong\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://fave.co/43FAw2m\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eGarmentory\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePR Representation:\u003c/strong\u003e In-house\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to ge